{"tid":2421201,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得返通宵/shift仲正過返office hour","createTime":"2021-02-24T10:55:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-01T01:22:08.000Z","uid":123613,"like":48,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"7f2a28c9ab6ca07c7bd6b911fd5547598dc63592","tid":2421201,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T10:55:13.000Z","msg":"而家份工輪住返office hour同通宵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n返office hour嗰個星期 12點幾瞓瞓6-7個鐘可以全日勁眼瞓 係得食飯嗰粒鐘同放工後先突然精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n搭車返工放工又係勁迫 仲要個人好頹 因為除咗放假之外喺屋企根本冇機會見到陽光咁滯 office又冇陽光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n反而返通宵嗰個星期 朝早同樣瞓6-7個鐘 但晏晝尾至成個夜晚都好精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 時間好似仲好用咗 夜晚返工又唔迫只係等車耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇人覺得返通宵/shift仲正過長返office hour<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e76dac1d53637ddb61fe5b98c424a20bede2b47b","tid":2421201,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T11:00:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"754544bfbb45be03e1dc180997817f5ee41f7743","tid":2421201,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T11:22:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b7951e86db81efec266104e5205b8de2149538d","tid":2421201,"uid":3694,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T11:32:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b63de446f748a53bf5a02c548c82593020ea30a9","tid":2421201,"uid":35361,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score